title: The Time is NOW!
author: Cheshirelulcat
pages:
#- The Time is Now

Brethren! Our economy is at a standstill. People cannot sell their goods, feed their families! Women and children go hungry whilst their men toil under th'oppressive regime. Their senators are corrupt, and vote based on economic
#- gain. The Ministers care not for the people nor for the state. They abuse their power to the fullest extent. Now is the time, my friends, to arise, arise from th'ashes of Prussian culture and be reborn into a new head of government : The Russian Empire.
#- 